        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p><addressee>Revd. Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="align(right)">
                <placeName>Balto.</placeName>
                <date>Nov. 12/62</date>
            </p>
            <p>Dear Sir,</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I intended long ago to an<lb/>swer your letter &amp; to transmit to
                you<lb/> the small amount which I owe you,<lb/> but sickness &amp; all kind of
                unprovided<lb/> disturbances, made me delay it till<lb/> to day. I hope therefore
                you will<lb/> excuse me.</p>
            <p>With regret I have seen by your<lb/> letter that you have also been sick,<lb/>
                <add>?</add> so is it with us...<add>אדם להבל דמה תהילים קמ”ד, ד</add><lb/> Thank to
                God, that you &amp; I, have<lb/> been restored to health &amp; spared per-<lb/>haps
                for a few years longer.</p>
            <p>In regard to your remark, that the<lb/> Occident for me was sent back to you</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>I can only assure you <add>לא ידעתי מי עשה הדבר הזה</add><lb/> for it would have been
                not only<lb/> against all courtesy, but even un-<lb/>grateful, for you have never
                charged<lb/> me anything for it, &amp; why should I<lb/> offend you &amp; be   ?
                    <add>משלם רע תחת טובה</add><lb/> I thought, that at this hard times<lb/> you
                don't send any more gratis<lb/> exemplars, &amp; I excused you perfectly,<lb/> but I
                have never sent any of your<lb/> copies back.</p>
            <p><sic>Inclosed</sic> please to <del>accept</del> receive<lb/> $6.15/100 as the pay for
                the books &amp; please<lb/> to send me again in <sic>Comission</sic></p>
            <p>4 Doz. first Catechism or Bible History</p>
            <p>4 “ Road to faith, by <persName>Nathan</persName></p>
            <p>4 “ Scriptures by <persName>Peixotto</persName></p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p>Please send them soon, &amp; without<lb/> expenses, &amp; as soon, as they shall
                be<lb/> sold, I will send you again the<lb/> amount.</p>
            <p>Wishing you perfect health &amp;<lb/>
                <add>כל טוב</add> I am</p>
            <p rend="indent(5)">Your faithful</p>
            <p rend="indent(6)">
                <persName role="author">A. Guinzburg</persName>
            </p>
        </body>
